    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-num">02</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Gesture Control</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">OK gesture to start. Palm to pause. V-sign to lock angle. Control your whole shoot from 10 meters away, no touching required.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card">
