    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-num">04</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Full 360° Freedom</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">Horizontal 360° with zero dead angle. Vertical 315° tilt. Flip between portrait and landscape with one tap. No limits.</p>
