    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-num">05</div>
      <div class="feat-title">All-Day Battery</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">1200mAh battery. 8 full hours of tracking. USB-C fast charging. Take it from morning workout to evening vlog without worrying.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-num">06</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Made for Every Platform</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">TikTok, Instagram Live, YouTube Shorts, Zoom, Twitch. Tripod mount included. Works on any flat surface or standard tripod.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

